item.title:
The New Jersey State Police is urging fans of Taylor Swift not to attend her shows at MetLife Stadium unless they have a ticket.
Swift’s #ErasTour has seen crowds of thousands without tickets gather to enjoy the show from outside the venue.

item.title:
‘Broken By Desire To Be Heavenly Sent’ by @LewisCapaldi debuts at #1 in the UK with 95,000 units, outselling the rest of the top 10 albums combined.
It becomes his second #1 album.
